'''達爾文日'''（{{lang-en|Darwin Day}}）是為了紀念[[博物学家|博物学家]]、[[生物學家|生物學家]][[查爾斯·達爾文|查爾斯·達爾文]]（生於1809年2月12日）而设立的节日，设立在每年的2月12日。在这一天，世界范围内都会举行庆祝和纪念活动<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url = http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&db=nfh&AN=2W63835285192&site=ehost-live|title = Darwin Day Celebration to Offer Evolution Education|last = |first = |date = 2015-02-07|work = The Knoxville News-Sentinel|access-date = 2015-05-07|via = |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518094826/http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&db=nfh&AN=2W63835285192&site=ehost-live|archive-date = 2015-05-18|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
查尔斯·达尔文于1882年4月19日去世，享年73岁。后世对他的纪念自那以后就开始出现。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timeanddate.com/holidays/fun/darwin-day|title=Fun Holiday – Darwin Day|website=www.timeanddate.com|language=en|access-date=2019-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331012016/https://www.timeanddate.com/holidays/fun/darwin-day|archive-date=2019-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>1909年，来自167个国家的400多名[[科学家|科学家]]和政要齐聚[[剑桥|剑桥]]，向达尔文的贡献致敬，并对最近的科学发现和相关理论展开了热烈的讨论。这次活动引起了被广泛报道，获得了公众关注。<ref>{{Cite web | last = van Wyhe | first = John | title = 1909: The first Darwin centenary | url = http://darwin-online.org.uk/1909.html | publisher = The Complete Works of Charles Darwin Online | accessdate = 2011-06-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611211504/http://darwin-online.org.uk/1909.html | archive-date = 2011-06-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1086/508076| title = The 1909 Darwin Celebration| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_isis_2006-09_97_3/page/447| journal = Isis| volume = 97| issue = 3| pages = 447| year = 2006| last1 = Richmond | first1 = M. L. }}</ref>同年2月12日，[[纽约科学院|纽约科学院]]在[[美国自然史博物馆|美国自然史博物馆]]举办了一场庆祝达尔文诞辰100周年和《[[物种起源|物种起源]]》出版50周年的活动，并揭幕了达尔文的半身铜像<ref>{{cite web| title = The Darwin Celebration| date = May 1909| url = http://www.naturalhistorymag.com/editors_pick/1909_03_pick.html| accessdate = 2007-09-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071009192128/http://www.naturalhistorymag.com/editors_pick/1909_03_pick.html| archive-date = 2007-10-09| dead-url = no}}</ref>。同年6月2日，[[新西兰皇家学会|新西兰皇家学会]]举办了一次“达尔文庆典”，据称“很多人参加”<ref>{{cite web | title= ''Transactions and Proceedings of the Royal Society of New Zealand 1868–1961'' | date= 1909 | url= http://rsnz.natlib.govt.nz/volume/rsnz_42/rsnz_42_02_007190.html | accessdate= 2007-09-17 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20070915131653/http://rsnz.natlib.govt.nz/volume/rsnz_42/rsnz_42_02_007190.html | archive-date= 2007-09-15 | dead-url= no }}</ref>。到了1959年，这年是达尔文诞辰150周年和《物种起源》出版100周年，世界范围内举行了{{le|1959年达尔文百年庆祝活动|Darwin Centennial Celebration (1959)|一系列庆祝活动}}。是年11月24日至28日，[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]举办了这一系列活动中最大的子活动。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ead.lib.uchicago.edu/view.xqy?id=ICU.SPCL.DARWIN100&c=d|title=Guide to the Darwin Centennial Celebration Records|last=|first=|date=|year=1959|website=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080125114431/http://ead.lib.uchicago.edu/view.xqy?id=ICU.SPCL.DARWIN100&c=d <!-- Bot retrieved archive -->|archivedate=2008-01-25|accessdate=2007-09-17}}</ref>

科学家和学者有时会在2月12日举办“{{lang|en|Phylum Feast}}”庆祝活动，在这种活动上，他们可以尽可能多地享用不同[[门_(生物)|门类]]生物制作的食物。在[[美国|美国]]，[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]{{le|塞勒姆州立大学|Salem State University}}自1980年以来每年举办一次“达尔文节”<ref>{{cite web | last =Kelly | first =Paul | title =2008 Darwin Festival | date =2003-04-22 | url =http://w3.salemstate.edu/~pkelly/darwin/ | accessdate =2007-08-01 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070804205456/http://w3.salemstate.edu/~pkelly/darwin/ | archive-date =2007-08-04 | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last =Kelly | first =Paul | title =History of the Darwin Festival | date =2006-12-19 | url =http://w3.salemstate.edu/~pkelly/darwin/history80s.htm | accessdate =2007-09-17 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20080121201153/http://w3.salemstate.edu/~pkelly/darwin/history80s.htm | archive-date =2008-01-21 | dead-url =no }}</ref>，并于2005年注册了“达尔文节”[[服务商标|服务商标]]<ref>{{cite web | last= USPTO | title= Trademark Electronic Search System (TESS) | date= 2007-08-31 | url= http://tess2.uspto.gov/bin/showfield?f=doc&state=jj4667.2.1 | accessdate= 2007-08-31 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090207013126/http://tess2.uspto.gov/bin/showfield?f=doc&state=jj4667.2.1 | archive-date= 2009-02-07 | dead-url= no }}</ref>。

